msContents.summary: Annotations attributed to the Palestinian rabbi and talmudist Bezalel ben Abraham Ashkenazi in a Venetian edition, printed in 1563 or 1564, of Bet Yosef, Joseph ben Ephraim Karo's commentary on Jacob ben Asher's legal treatise Arba'ah turim.
